  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a blender, combine tahini, lemon juice, garlic, and sumac, and blend until smooth.",
    "In a Korean brass bowl, arrange a layer of toasted pita bread.",
    "Top the pita bread with a layer of dehydrated herring fillets.",
    "Drizzle the tahini sauce over the herring fillets.",
    "Sprinkle chopped pickled turnips and parsley over the top.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional parsley if desired.",
    "Let the dish rest for 10 minutes before serving to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Refrigerate any leftovers and consume within 24 hours."
